                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Aussie attack
                            
	Melbourne, March 2 (PTI): A Sri Lankan and his Indian wife were attacked and racially abused here, the incident coming to light on a day Australian foreign minister Stephen Smith was in Delhi promising steps against such assaults.        
	A group of 25 drunken thugs, most of them white men, bashed up 60-year-old Ranjit Sahasranaman and Agalya Sahasranaman, outside their Melbourne home on Sunday morning.                                                                                                                                                                       
